People in Brazil came out in protest against President Dilma Rousseff on Sunday, while pro-government demonstrators marched earlier in the week on Thursday. Did you take part in either of the events? Perhaps you were at a different one protesting with Comperj workers outside Petrobas HQ in Rio de Janeiro on Monday? Or are you planning a demonstration in the future? We’d like to see your photos, videos and hear your experiences.Share your view of Brazil in photos, videos and words by clicking on the blue ‘Contribute’ button on this article. You can also use the GuardianWitness smartphone app or the new Guardian app – just search for ‘GuardianWitness assignments’. You can also email guardian.witness@theguardian.comWe’ll publish the the most interesting contributions on the Guardian site Compartilhe sua visão do Brasil em fotos, vídeos e palavras clicando no botão azul “Contribute” neste artigo. Você também pode usar o aplicativo de smartphone GuardianWitness ou o novo aplicativo do Guardian e procurar por “GuardianWitness assignments”. Ou, você pode nos enviar um email pelo guardian.witness@theguardian.com Nós publicaremos as contribuições mais interessantes em nosso site.